src:
元元披白紗甜喊「我們結婚了！」　新郎身分曝光
02 Nov 2019, 08:27 by 梁欣喬
擁有E奶魔鬼身材女星「元元」吳婕安，昨（1日）突然在IG上傳婚紗照，甜喊「我們結婚了！」讓粉絲驚喜萬分，新郎到底是誰？結果…竟然令人意外，原來竟是「國民初戀女友」之稱的林莎。
在IG照片中看到元元紮起公主頭，身穿白色低胸爆乳婚紗，簡直美翻了。擁有美麗胸器的她，胸前深V讓北半球呼之欲出，合身剪裁更凸顯纖細腰身，大秀火辣身材，手上還拿著捧花，對著鏡頭露出嬌羞甜笑。


元元紮起公主頭身穿上白色低胸爆乳婚紗，簡直美翻了。（翻攝自元元IG）

而坐在一旁的不是新郎「倌」，而是有「國民初戀女友」之稱的林莎，也打扮得美美現身。她頭戴皇冠，身穿純白削肩禮服，露出性感鎖骨，元元在貼文甜喊「小寶今天好像韓劇女主角超美！她昨天說要娶我，結果我們今天登記了！歡迎祝福我們！經過一個禮拜真心愛上妳」。


元元的新郎並不是男友，而是有「國民初戀女友」之稱的林莎。（翻攝自元元IG）

不做作的元元個性深受觀眾喜愛，被封為「新呆萌教主」，她先前在節目中與小鬼（黃鴻升）氣氛曖昧，還戲稱自己是「鬼嫂」引發關注，再加上常在社群上曬照分享生活，社交網站有高達56萬的追隨者，人氣十分高。
更新時間｜2019.11.02 08:25
text:
Yuan Yuan daisy sweet shout "We are married!" Groom identity exposure
02 Nov 2019, 08:27 by Liang Xinqiao
Wu Yi'an, who owns the E milk devil figure, "Yuan Yuan", suddenly uploaded a wedding photo in IG yesterday (1st), sweetly shouting "We are married!" Surprise the fans, who is the groom? As a result, it turned out to be surprising. It turned out to be Lin Sha, who is known as the "national first love girlfriend."
In the IG photo, I saw Yuan Yuan praying the princess head, wearing a white low-cut burst wedding dress, it was beautiful. She has a beautiful chest, her deep chest V makes the northern hemisphere come out, and the tailoring cuts the slim waist. The big show is hot and the hands are holding the bouquet, showing a shy smile to the camera.


Yuan Yuan tied up the princess and wore a white low-cut burst wedding dress, which was simply beautiful. (Revolving from Yuan IG)

Sitting on the side is not the bridegroom "倌", but Lin Sha, who is known as the "national first love girlfriend", is also dressed up beautifully. She wears a crown and wears a pure white shoulder-shoulder dress, revealing a sexy collarbone. Yuan Yuan is screaming in the post. "Xiaobao seems to be a super hero in the Korean drama today! She said that she wanted to marry me yesterday. As a result, we registered today! Welcome to bless us. After a week, I really fell in love with you."


The Yuan Yuan’s groom is not a boyfriend, but Lin Sha, who is known as the “national first love girlfriend”. (Revolving from Yuan IG)

The unconventional elementary personality is deeply loved by the audience and has been named as "new buddy master." She used to sneak into the atmosphere of the devil (Huang Hongsheng) in the show, and also nicknamed herself as a "ghost", which is often caused by concern. Sharing life on the community, social networking sites have as many as 560,000 followers, very popular.
